{"tid":2510600,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"《有圖慎入》想請教下醫療巴絲有冇人知咩事","createTime":"2021-04-30T09:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T10:43:36.000Z","uid":369179,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0d86967de7815fbf570d4efc74c91023509cab81","tid":2510600,"uid":369179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"啱啱除低條褲去大便突然見到左腳大髀內側有大量大大小小不同分佈既紅點，佢哋唔痕又唔痛，但見到真係幾驚，怕係啲唔知咩免疫系統問題嘅徵兆。<br />\n<br />\n我係男仔黎，咁發病位置就只係得左腳大髀內側先有，check晒身體其他部份都見到佢哋蹤跡。而本人皮膚狀況應該算係偏乾嘅敏感肌，皮膚狀態本身就好麻麻，手臂等等地方有好嚴重嘅油脂粒問題。而生活習慣方面每一日無論有冇出街都會沖涼，但本身有時食無定時同埋偏夜瞓，唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求求各位唔該幫我睇睇，睇吓嚴唔嚴重，同埋知唔知發生咩事，小弟好驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，本身有嘢忙緊，諗住見到面積擴大先睇醫生，但係問題如果真係太嚴重就會即刻睇醫生，唔該巴打絲打幫幫忙，感激感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1QGw3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1QGw3w.png&h=1e0f0643&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xdjgkWV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxdjgkWV.png&h=28a88fd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"618ba3b6a33aeeceeba4119e676c4eee2d2b5d53","tid":2510600,"uid":369179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"（補充）本人係毒撚嚟，完全冇性經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fa441df84885e7b491c1a6866519c9fdc04831","tid":2510600,"uid":262053,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"你唔識去睇醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b2c38a78db040d0c016ba632484c2f8a03298c","tid":2510600,"uid":369179,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"54fa441df84885e7b491c1a6866519c9fdc04831","tid":2510600,"uid":262053,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"你唔識去睇醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"因為最近有好重要嘅嘢忙緊，而且又係啱啱發現，所以諗住上網問一問人，同埋睇定少少先，如果發現真係情況真係好嚴重，或者見到佢有惡化嘅話先即刻睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a49fee4ad97a754408228ee07aa6ef52a093d87","tid":2510600,"uid":105515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"以前做完引體上升<br />\n兩隻手掌都會類似咁樣<br />\n唔知係咪d微絲血管爆左"},{"pid":"55dae2c62bbdc2073ca97c76c4232e9e6d7caa56","tid":2510600,"uid":374831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:30:59.000Z","msg":"你上得來問多預咗啲人覆你下世小心啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係醫生都唔會睇你一兩張圖就知係咩病啦 驚嘅咪快啲去睇醫生"},{"pid":"43036e10de382055798becffd73ee0115ec09189","tid":2510600,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:45:59.000Z","msg":"搭單問，發燒發到40度，請問我應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9868d0d7acb77767fcd6fade726cd041a4d9ab9b","tid":2510600,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"蕁痲疹"},{"pid":"6447c615804c20ead0779565f2e2455c5cc63953","tid":2510600,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"100%蕁痲疹<br />\n<br />\n我自己出過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似有血紅點係皮膚上<br />\n又唔痕又唔痛<br />\n皮膚一樣咁平"},{"pid":"b38ced708d0fe5cc3ee372fb8bd2e854197a9f2e","tid":2510600,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"性病啦"},{"pid":"cfd9c3d61f24398a25e7b0d24778c260fd7048b4","tid":2510600,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:27:13.000Z","msg":"記錯左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係蕁痲疹<br />\n係微絲血管爆裂先岩"},{"pi